{"tid":2229284,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"android撚終於唔使畀airdrop邊緣化","createTime":"2020-10-04T09:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T08:42:05.000Z","uid":329733,"like":9,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"c874c9b3d5a1e463fa67538b21f2d6172bfeb5f6","tid":2229284,"uid":329733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"我見連登冇人講<br />\n支01唔貼link<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNearby Share咫尺共享懶人包｜Android版AirDrop實測與使用教學<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAndroid 新功能 Nearby Share 咫尺共享，是 Google 再一次挑戰 Apple 及 iPhone 的 AirDrop。這一個 Android 版的短距無線檔案傳送功能，可以讓用戶跟附近的聯絡人輕易分享各種檔案，似乎 Android 用戶終於可以有一個可靠自家的 AirDrop！<br />\n<br />\nNearby Share（中文：咫尺共享 ）可以說是繼 Files Go 之後，Google 再一次在 Android 平台上，提供類似 iPhone iOS 平台及 Apple 的 macOS 平台共通的 AirDrop 短距無線檔案傳送功能。Files Go 雖然功能上已經非常完整，但由於需要用戶安裝的關係，就算在 Android 用戶之間的普及度一直都不高。<br />\n<br />\nAndroid Nearby Share 可以說是 Android 版的 AirDrop，Android 用戶之間，終於有一個可以輕易分享檔案的短距無線傳送方案。（蔡浩騰 攝）<br />\nAndroid Nearby Share 可以說是 Android 版的 AirDrop，Android 用戶之間，終於有一個可以輕易分享檔案的短距無線傳送方案。（蔡浩騰 攝）<br />\n<br />\n今次 Nearby Share 毋須安裝，亦毋須透過系統升級加入，僅需要 Google Play Service 派送，現時已經開始支援 Pixel 系列、部份 Samsung 及 Asus 等的手機，而且更加會支援 Android 6.0 平台以上的所有裝置，大大提升普及率。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 方面表示，Nearby Share 功能將會在未來數星期派送至所有支援的 Android 裝置，換言之大家就算想急住用，都係要等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對比起 AirDrop，Nearby Share 暫時似乎只可以搜尋及跟自己已儲存的聯絡人分享檔案，不過 Google 有提及，Nearby Share 將支援匿名傳送及接收檔案（似乎是類似短距檔案廣播的功能），不過詳細的使用情況，就要留待日後的更新再作觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNearby Share 除支援 Android 平台外，亦會於未來數月加入對 Chromebook 的支援。不過，雖然 Google 未有表示 Nearby Share 將來支援 Chrome 瀏覽器的可能性，不過從近年 Android 對 Chrome 瀏覽器的支援，在不久的將來能夠從 Mac 或者 Windows 電腦的 Chrome 瀏覽器中接收 Nearby Share 檔案，大家亦不用覺得出奇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLc0s0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLc0s0e.jpg&h=a615d8be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nandroid撚喺一大班人share相嘅時候, 唔使係一邊玩泥沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過中文<span class=\"red\">咫尺共享</span>真係好撚難聽"},{"pid":"54b7898287411bb7f3a86cb7a3eee1ca675b4e37","tid":2229284,"uid":46151,"like":29,"dislike":12,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:15:23.000Z","msg":"an本身都大撚把方法share files<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2cd3b2f87a95c43ec7264922528e0fd57f0f9ef","tid":2229284,"uid":329733,"like":9,"dislike":21,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"54b7898287411bb7f3a86cb7a3eee1ca675b4e37","tid":2229284,"uid":46151,"like":29,"dislike":12,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:15:23.000Z","msg":"an本身都大撚把方法share files<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:20:58.000Z","msg":"咁你咁講ios都係啦<br />\n問題係android缺乏一種好似airdrop咁<br />\n短距離又唔使網絡嘅匿名分享方式"},{"pid":"d979f8f85b9ea18723f642e757d21c895d07998f","tid":2229284,"uid":48286,"like":73,"dislike":4,"score":69,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:33:24.000Z","msg":"你都戇鳩鳩，圍住你嗰啲人都用iPhone邊個些俾你姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪又係邊緣化"},{"pid":"1f087fdcd191f4d13c29b14d519a752ac551d2e0","tid":2229284,"uid":143151,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:34:13.000Z","msg":"其實冇分別 都係收唔air drop <br />\n大家各自圍爐"},{"pid":"336faaf9a1cf9b5d8efed675b155c25595179726","tid":2229284,"uid":31215,"like":8,"dislike":51,"score":-43,"quote":{"pid":"d979f8f85b9ea18723f642e757d21c895d07998f","tid":2229284,"uid":48286,"like":73,"dislike":4,"score":69,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:33:24.000Z","msg":"你都戇鳩鳩，圍住你嗰啲人都用iPhone邊個些俾你姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪又係邊緣化"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"其實而家iPhone少人用咗好多"},{"pid":"ba0e586975c0bba7a42dbf