,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:51:23.000Z","msg":"你咁講就合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbc5a9c12a9c15c8b01244747b66f1f17dca897","tid":2229284,"uid":229793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6a6bda1cf7092f721981fb6d53eb1cb6033b85f0","tid":2229284,"uid":283,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:47:13.000Z","msg":"android亂咁收野<br />\n驚佢SEND D毒過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:55:32.000Z","msg":"除左on9 我都唔知話你咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42c9fb9cfcca3c54a944cffc3da88d0aa18bbbb","tid":2229284,"uid":229793,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:56:34.000Z","msg":"新聞post 變左做毒撚idog飛機post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d004581adb585d943dbc55a2da76554d545bc00","tid":2229284,"uid":34874,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"037f2b86e00047a062990065218c45054914ae08","tid":2229284,"uid":5220,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:47:59.000Z","msg":"An撚咁鍾意熄嘢點用呢個功能啊<br />\n搞咗十分鐘都send唔出，最後發現係熄咗WiFi/BT<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"一撳開啟就自動開晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4L9mAs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4L9mAs.png&h=542f4293&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8eecaf96ead61af45a93b4967ef2541f0e6fa340","tid":2229284,"uid":29167,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"無得cross platform 都係無乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成堆friend 有幾可an 機佔多數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：雙修"},{"pid":"fae51f01b2b54128e963d5aa381af962b3279eef","tid":2229284,"uid":250177,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"14c540d282098f0329c980d88910d08a3a33509e","tid":2229284,"uid":329733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d5f98e509ccb429a26b6f0c4494cc29f5e503a3","tid":2229284,"uid":250177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:42:35.000Z","msg":"老實說，暫時唔太睇好Nearby share <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/handup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 手機 Android 派<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:26:10.000Z","msg":"主要喺Android 喺一個開源嘅系統，唔似ios <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大部分Android 手機廠商，都會客製化自家的手機rom(除咗pixel 與Android One 系統)，客製化自然會附加一啲自煮開發程式 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如自家雲端連結，或者跨品牌嘅資料交換服務(華為, Oppo, 小米 同埋某兩間公司，已經有一個跨品牌嘅小圈子share)<br />\n雲端上載同埋小圈子嘅share, 一定會listening某個group 嘅port，而嗰啲port 有可能同Nearby share 的port 衝突 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如A 君用華為手機，華為cloud 可能長期listen 10001 port, 而Nearby share 使用時，咁啱又需要10001 port, 結果用Nearby 同人哋交換時出現問題，就瀨Android 個Nearby 廢，send 唔倒嘢，但喺其實問題出喺華為cloud 嗰邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n冇理由因為你自家程式亂用port, 就要google 遷就你㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外有啲手機有類似防火牆的功能，覺得個文件 / 程式有危險就block 咗你，搞到share 個文件都要過五關斬六將咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有Android 的手機有平有貴，wifi 同埋bluebooth 硬件品質參差，send packet 話斷就斷，連問題都唔會知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nApple 因為型號統一，就算有問題都可以輕鬆改<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(手機回覆，打到1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"a389ac63c65e2de55a33a057921a1116d0706448","tid":2229284,"uid":48631,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"我用部iphone11 pro max同影完合照之後即刻開airdrop share返d相畀班friend<br />\n唯獨是有一個android 小毒撚share唔到畀佢，佢細細聲走埋嚟問我「pizza哥，可唔可以whatsapp返d相畀我？」<br />\n我話「whatsapp壓縮完之後懞到連人樣都分唔清，畀左你都冇用啦」<br />\n「咁不如藍牙send畀我呀，又話者email都得架...我email係iluvmisspun@gmail.com...」<br />\n最後我都冇理到佢，因為我諗一個fb淨係立場新聞post，ig淨係用嚟follow d大波妹嘅人要張合照嚟都冇乜用<br />\n但後來我諗諗下，佢應該係想要張合照相嚟J olivia，就係𠴱個影合照嘅時候企喺我隔離搵對波un住我手臂𠴱個olivia，un到我而家隻手仲有少少痛，講起都嬲嬲地..."}],"pinned":{"pid":"9fd8e51a2a73020541947170c4503aaf96e32a52","tid":2229284,"uid":156096,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>華為又贏</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連Nearby Share都無得用"}}